## ğŸ¨ DESIGN SYSTEM (USE THESE COLORS, NO OTHERS)

### Color Palette (from INSANE-3D-UIUX-Concept.md)
```
Primary:
- Gold: #FFD700, #FFC700, #FFB700
- Teal: #00D9FF, #00B8CC, #008899
- Purple: #9D4EDD, #7B2FBF, #5A189A

Accent:
- Deep Blue: #001F3F
- Cyan: #00FFFF (glow, not main)
- Magenta: #FF006E (danger, alerts)

Neutrals:
- Dark BG: #0A0E27 (dark mode)
- Light BG: #F5F7FA (light mode)
- Dark Text: #1A1A2E
- Light Text: #E8E8FF
- Subtle Border: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1) (gold with transparency)

Gradients:
- Hero: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD700, #9D4EDD)
- Dark Surface: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A0E27, #1A1A2E)
- Glow: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.2), transparent)
```

### Spacing Scale (Tailwind default + custom)
```
4px, 8px, 12px, 16px, 20px, 24px, 32px, 40px, 48px, 64px
(Use: space-1, space-2, space-3, space-4, space-5, space-6, space-8, space-10, space-12, space-16)
```

### Typography Scale
```
Display: 3xl (36px), 2xl (30px)
Heading: xl (20px), lg (18px), base (16px)
Body: base (14px), sm (12px)
Caption: xs (12px), tiny (10px)
Monospace: Fira Code, SF Mono, Menlo (for code blocks)
```

### Shadows & Effects
```
sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)
md: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)
lg: 0 10px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2)
glow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.3)
glow-gold: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2)
```

### Border Radius
```
sm: 4px
base: 6px
md: 8px
lg: 12px
full: 9999px
