## ğŸ¨ ANIMATION SPECIFICATIONS

### Entrance Animations
```
Cards: Fade in + slide up 30px (staggered, 100ms delay)
Timing: 400ms ease-out (cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1))
Text: Character-by-character reveal (GSAP SplitText)
Numbers: Count up animation (0 â†’ final value in 800ms)
```

### Hover Animations
```
Cards: Scale 1.02, shadow increase, border glow
Timing: 200ms ease-out
Buttons: Background color shift, scale 1.05, shadow increase
Links: Underline slide, color change
```

### Scroll Animations
```
Headlines: Text skew effect (Lusion style)
Parallax: Elements move at different speeds
Reveal: Elements fade in as they enter viewport
Timing: Tied to scroll position, responsive
```

### Transition Animations
```
Page changes: Fade out (200ms) â†’ Fade in (200ms)
Modal opens: Scale from 90% â†’ 100%, blur backdrop
Modal closes: Scale to 95%, blur backdrop
Drawer slides: From right edge, 300ms ease-out
```

### 60FPS Requirements
```
âœ… Use CSS transforms (translateX, translateY, scale, rotate)
âœ… Avoid animating width/height/margin (use transform instead)
âœ… Use will-change: transform on animated elements
âœ… Debounce scroll events (max 60fps)
âœ… Use requestAnimationFrame for JS animations
âœ… Test on low-end devices (60 FPS check in DevTools)
```

