## ğŸŒ FRONTEND ARCHITECTURE

### State Management (Zustand)
```tsx
Store structure:
â”œâ”€â”€ ui (dark mode, sidebar open, modal state)
â”œâ”€â”€ auth (user, token, permissions)
â”œâ”€â”€ drift (drifts list, filters, sorting, pagination)
â”œâ”€â”€ alerts (alerts list, unread count, filters)
â”œâ”€â”€ notifications (toast notifications)
â””â”€â”€ cache (cached API responses, invalidation)
```

### API Integration (React Query + Axios)
```tsx
Endpoints:
GET /api/v1/drifts              // Get all drifts with pagination
GET /api/v1/drifts/:id          // Get single drift details
POST /api/v1/drifts/:id/approve // Approve remediation
POST /api/v1/drifts/:id/reject  // Reject remediation
GET /api/v1/metrics             // Dashboard metrics
GET /api/v1/cost/trend          // Cost chart data
GET /api/v1/alerts              // Get alerts
WS /api/v1/ws                   // WebSocket for real-time updates
```

### Custom Hooks
```tsx
useDrifts()           // Fetch + manage drifts list
useDriftDetails(id)   // Fetch single drift
useCostTrend()        // Fetch cost chart data
useAlerts()           // Fetch alerts + real-time
useAuth()             // User authentication
useDarkMode()         // Dark/light mode toggle
useNotifications()    // Toast notifications
useWindowSize()       // Responsive helpers
useClickOutside()     // Close modals on outside click
useFocusTrap()        // Focus management in modals
```

