## ğŸ“± RESPONSIVE DESIGN SPECIFICATIONS

### Breakpoints (Tailwind)
```
Mobile: 0-640px        (sm: 640px)
Tablet: 640-1024px     (md: 768px, lg: 1024px)
Desktop: 1024px+       (xl: 1280px, 2xl: 1536px)
```

### Mobile-First Strategy
```
1. Design for mobile first (375px width)
2. Add tablet styles at md: 768px
3. Add desktop styles at lg: 1024px
4. Test on: iPhone 12 (390px), iPad (768px), MacBook (1440px)
```

### Responsive Components
```
Hero Section:
  Mobile: 60vh, text centered, smaller 3D (or disable 3D, show static image)
  Desktop: 100vh, 3D mesh visible

Grid Layouts:
  Mobile: 1 column
  Tablet: 2 columns
  Desktop: 3 columns

Sidebar:
  Mobile: Hidden (drawer on hamburger click)
  Desktop: Always visible

Charts:
  Mobile: 100% width, single metric visible
  Desktop: Full visualization
```

