## ğŸš€ PERFORMANCE CHECKLIST

```
âœ… Images: Next/Image with srcset, lazy loading
âœ… Code splitting: Dynamic imports for heavy components
âœ… Bundle size: <100KB JS gzipped for initial page
âœ… First Contentful Paint (FCP): <1.5s
